<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上，当别人都睡着了，小美人鱼会登上王宫阳台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那里，她看见海上的波浪，想起在海底的家人们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天晚上，她看见她的姐姐们在远处的海里游泳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们想念亲爱的小妹妹。” 大姐大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她当然不能回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她想：“我也想你们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，我要和王子结婚，幸福地生活在地上世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她跟姐姐们挥手时，她们认出了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们游近岩石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她伸出双臂，告诉她们，如果她可以，她会拥抱姐姐们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那以后，她们几乎每晚都来给妹妹唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一次，她甚至看见了智慧人鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>智慧人鱼已经好多年没游到过海面上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼的父亲——海底国王，也和奶奶一起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也朝她伸出双臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的奶奶好像在说：“我们想你，我亲爱的孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，小美人鱼还是想得到灵魂，想和王子在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢和你在一起，小伙伴。” 王子经常这么说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你对我来说很宝贵。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，王子从来没说过要跟她结婚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他好像把我当朋友，但是我要和她结婚。” 小美人鱼想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果他和别人结婚，我就会变成波浪上的泡沫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想到那样的命运，她颤抖着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候，小美人鱼会用眼睛恳求王子：“请爱我吧，我想做你最爱的女人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她那么看着他时，王子会用双臂拥抱她，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像哥哥一样亲了亲她的额头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，小美人鱼希望这能改变。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，王后对国王说：“王子该结婚了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她希望王子能跟邻国的一位公主结婚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们安排他们见面吧。” 她告诉国王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当王子听到这个消息，他摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想跟那个公主结婚，小伙伴。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只会跟我真爱的人结婚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他给小美人鱼讲了他的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“几年前，在暴风雨中，我坐的船沉了，我差点儿死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>幸好我被冲到了海边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当我睁开眼睛，我看见一个少女救了我的命。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的名字叫梅丹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把我带到了附近的教堂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当我第二天醒过来时，她离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然我只见过她一面，但她就是我唯一的真爱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除非我找不到她，否则我绝不会结婚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，是我救了你的！” 小美人鱼想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请你试着去理解。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，王子无法理解，只是对着她微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，小伙伴，别因为我的故事而伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>即使我永远也找不到她，有你在我身边，我也很幸福。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果他知道真相该多好啊。” 她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天，王子会明白我比其他任何人更爱他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，到时候他就会跟我结婚的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼不得不再忍耐一段时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>